channel.title: Unreliable Oscillator, yet another random subpatch/object from Debterminer
channel.description: UnreliableOscillator.axs (11.6 KB) What does it do? It oscillates. How does it work? I have no idea. Whats it sound like? Well... erm kind of terrible sometimes. It can make very strange haunting noises, it does not track keyboard well at all. It was not what i intended to make, but the results were interesting enough that i felt i should share them.
